highlights.text: “One Of My Life” by BLVCKHEART and K6Y has been on Viral Songs Thailand the longest, at 251 days straight.
“TABOLA BALE” by Silet Open Up, Jacson Seran, Juan Reza, and Diva Aurel is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Thailand, up 14 spots at #83.
YUNGTARR has the most spots on Viral Songs Thailand. “OMW” is the highest at #28.
